Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此勞空候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}つくばねの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望築波嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 都怪你不說抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶到了 搶到了 搶到一張了 繼續加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 連我都在敵陣搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼能輸在進攻上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下一次一定要搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在個人戰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張牌也就只是一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}こひぞつもりて ふちとなりぬる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相思積歲月 早已化深潭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要為隊伍搶下一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わすらるる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誓遭遺忘
