Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡路來千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みよしのの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故國秋風起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好 西田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決勝字的變化我是絕對不會弄錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成為大家的脊樑骨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いかにひさしき ものとかはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迢迢怨遙夜 問君安可知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}失誤什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算一次也不行
