Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜夜相思苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞澤一勝
