Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞澤兩勝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張一張地搶過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾瀨 棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓它就這樣結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我還有比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 你得躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽已經棄權了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 不行啦 老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了也沒用 比賽已經回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家約好要勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對不起 大家 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊 千早 你不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾瀨 我今天第一次贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 而且還是二連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在決賽中輸給了富士崎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還想再來幾場比賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾瀨身體沒法馬上恢復的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐明天一早的新幹線回去怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興奮到現在還是按耐不住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以完美的狀態出席明天的個人戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若宮詩暢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上最年輕的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさそふ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿院非白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是這種展開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經相差10張牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然她跟若宮詩暢完全不是一個級別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女生也快要喪失鬥志了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是是千早盯上的牌的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該也能以不輸女王的速度搶到才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 場上的牌有數十張之多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想全方位的盯緊是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道女王可以做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像不到 自己勝利的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次碰到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要拿到一張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能在精神上輸給12歲的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはえの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難波葦節短
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說速度接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふくからに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枯焦憐草木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20號在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僵硬的身體…動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想動得更快… 更自由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在競技線當中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算眼前是足以令身體僵硬的強勁對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能自由地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然無法說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「強勁」就是這麼一回事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果… 只拿到5張而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和女王之間 相差20張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直線… 筆直的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直… 更快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不背誦得更完美 就無法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背誦 背誦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直 更快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直 更快 聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加…更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎樣做才能贏她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早的夢想此刻終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為真正的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:56.50,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(138,311)}女子之間的秘密1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小千和小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要跟歌牌部的人交往 你們選誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:56.50,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(344,163)}同學小滿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我想這個根本不用問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.89,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(390,122)}祝 一枝獨秀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝賀你 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.64,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(136,307)}女子之間的秘密2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:09.64,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,138)}想談談戀愛話題的小滿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是跟男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟男孩子交往的話 選誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用限定歌牌部也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以認真地回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會影響本篇進展的 還是不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.95,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(354.511,186.741)\frz262.2}還沒結束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用四字熟語來表述一下朋友的形像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:44.49,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(817,207)}就算沒有在這個單元出場 我也不會在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.49,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(494,281)}一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不要再說什麼烤肉定食了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駒野嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭腦明晰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小奏是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才色兼備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駒野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眉目秀麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豬突猛進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個來形容千早就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉包君是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,養豚狗肉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想說羊頭狗肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但為什麼是這個詞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是想不到別的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 綾瀨你剛才幹麼說我是豬…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 今年也請大家多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,207)}我覺得 記不全百人一首的人 就是一隻蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:34.99,xs1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(167,253)\frz262.924}下週再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.55,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.93,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:51.10,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.98,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.73,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:05.07,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:12.91,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:18.25,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:24.05,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.93,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:33.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.55,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走過回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.93,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微風輕輕吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:51.10,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}閒話家常也異常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.98,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依舊一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.73,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我們常常相約等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:05.07,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然記得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:12.91,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在我心懷強烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:18.25,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}有什麼在目標之處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:24.05,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在的話似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.93,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}試著伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:33.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在夢想的路上終有一天會再度重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.83,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}行くあてない街
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:36.08,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}ひとり先を歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:41.34,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夕日に照らされた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:46.43,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}失いそうな心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:51.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}変わってゆくなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:56.31,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}想いもしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.57,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君と重ねた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:06.61,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}いつの間に違う方へと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:10.37,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}歩いてたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:15.75,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:20.75,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}遠すぎる世界見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:26.18,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ほら 響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:33.47,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌 この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.83,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}向著無名的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:36.08,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}形單影隻地前進著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:41.34,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}被夕陽照得通紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:46.43,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}近乎要遺失的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:51.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}卻逐漸發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:56.31,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我萬萬也沒有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.57,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}與你在一起的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:06.61,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}不覺之間我們卻已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:10.37,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}走向了不同的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:15.75,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻你我兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:20.75,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著遙不可及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:26.18,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻 你瞧 歌聲響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:33.47,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你曾經教會我唱的歌謠 迴響於這片天空
